{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Knights Within</strong> is being developed by <strong>Indecision Labs</strong>, a solo developer working on their first public project.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/KW_Gif1.gif?t=1731980729\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/KWv2_Underline.png?t=1731980729\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/KW_TextHeader_WeAreAllThatsLeft.png?t=1731980729\" />Humanity is fighting for survival against the wraiths that now reign dominant in the world. Thankfully, technology is on our side. Fight your way through hordes of enemies while completing objectives to further mankind's struggle to survive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/KW_TextHeader_SurviveTheHorde.png?t=1731980729\" />Embark on procedurally generated missions to push back the threat of the Wraiths. Progressing through a mission grants randomized modifiers for both you and your enemies. The longer you survive, the crazier the powers get, keeping each run fresh and unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/KW_TextHeader_CraftYourKnight.png?t=1731980729\" />Create your own class by equipping gear mods for your various weapons and armor to enhance your preferred playstyle. As one of the prestigious knights protecting humanity, you have access to the most technologically advanced equipment available. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/KW_Gif3.gif?t=1731980729\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/KW_TextHeader_PlaySoloOrCoop.png?t=1731980729\" />Run missions by yourself, or bring up to 3 friends to fight alongside you against the never ending hordes of enemies in your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/KW_TextHeader_EndlessDifficulty.png?t=1731980729\" />Play the default mission based mode, completing objectives while struggling to survive. Or try the Gauntlet mode, where your stage progress is saved and the difficulty scales endlessly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/KW_TextHeader_WeWillEndure.png?t=1731980729\" />Knights Within is a hack&amp;slash horde shooter with rogue-lite elements. Design custom loadouts, navigate procedurally generated levels and utilize random power-ups. Either solo or with friends, can you survive endless waves of enemies to ensure humanity's survival?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/KW_Gif2.gif?t=1731980729\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2406180/extras/KWv2_Underline.png?t=1731980729\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Rank 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2406180/1c9b3527768293bbf2fd29e4c289dea1ffc127b5.jpg"},{"name":"Rank 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2406180/1c9b3527768293bbf2fd29e4c289dea1ffc127b5.j